# DevMesh Node Configuration
# Copy to nodes.conf and edit for your infrastructure
#
# Format: IP NODE_NAME API_HOST SSH_USER
#
# API_HOST should be the IP where the DevMesh API is running (port 8000)
# If nodes are on different subnets, use the appropriate API IP for each
#
# Example for multi-subnet setup:
#   - Nodes on 10.0.0.x use API at 10.0.0.20
#   - Nodes on 192.168.1.x use API at 192.168.1.184 (same server, different interface)

# Example entries (uncomment and edit):
# 10.0.0.19   gpu-node          10.0.0.20       myuser
# 10.0.0.18   db-server         10.0.0.20       root
# 192.168.1.50 remote-node      192.168.1.10    admin
